data.description: Welcome to this lavish renovated townhome, nestled in the heart of Naples. The moment you walk through the door, you are greeted by a sense of Luxury with quality finishes & touches throughout. The open floor plan seamlessly blends the living and dining areas, providing an ideal space for hosting & relaxation.The well appointed kitchen is an entertainer's dream, featuring pristine brand-new Quartz countertops, white cabinetry & quality appliances. Natural light pours in through large windows, creating an inviting atmosphere that complements the stunning interior & brand-new flooring throughout. The primary suite is a true sanctuary, boasting a spacious en-suite bathroom with a walk-in shower & dual vanities while the two additional bedrooms offer ample space for family or overnight guests. Step outside to the private screened lanai, where a tranquil setting awaits. The home is situated within an exclusive gated community offering a clubhouse, pool/spa & picnic area. With easy access to pristine beaches, world-class golf courses, phenomenal schools and fine dining establishments, this luxurious property presents an unmatched opportunity to embrace the Naples lifestyle!
